---
---

<section class="founders">
  <div class="founders__container">
    <div class="founders__image fade-up">
      <img
        src="/images/founder.webp"
        alt="Grundarna av GASTRO|nome i köket"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        width="480"
        height="360"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="founders__content fade-up delay-1">
      <span class="founders__eyebrow">Sedan 2009</span>
      <h2 class="founders__title">Med passion<br />för matupplevelser</h2>
      <p class="founders__text">
        GASTRO|nome grundades med en enkel vision — att skapa en plats där god mat,
        varmt värdskap och äkta gemenskap möts. Sedan dess har vi vuxit, men hjärtat
        är detsamma.
      </p>
      <p class="founders__signature">— Grundarna av GASTRO|nome</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .founders {
    padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem) 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg, #FAFAF9);
  }

  .founders__container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .founders__image {
    display: inline-block;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .founders__image img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 480px;
    height: auto;
    filter: grayscale(0.1);
  }

  .founders__content {
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .founders__eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent, #8B6F47);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .founders__title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--color-text, #1A1A1A);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .founders__text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #6B6B6B);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .founders__signature {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent, #8B6F47);
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
